WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.174
The clinical stakes are high.

00:00:02.174 --> 00:00:05.217
Twenty to thirty percent develop acute heart

00:00:05.217 --> 00:00:05.652
failure.

00:00:05.652 --> 00:00:08.696
Ventricular tachycardia, fibrillation, and complete heart block

00:00:08.696 --> 00:00:10.870
drive sudden cardiac death risk.

00:00:10.870 --> 00:00:13.478
Fulminant cases arrive in cardiogenic shock.

00:00:13.478 --> 00:00:16.522
Up to thirty percent progress to chronic

00:00:16.522 --> 00:00:19.565
dilated cardiomyopathy, and mural thrombus raises embolic

00:00:19.565 --> 00:00:20.000
risk.
